select  to_char(to_date('2021','yyyy') + interval '1 year' * a.inter,'yyyy')||'01010000' as strdt      
        ,to_char(to_date('2021','yyyy') + interval '1 year' * a.inter,'yyyy')||'12312359' as enddt     
   from (                                                                                              
 select                                                                                                
        generate_series(                                                                               
                         0,                                                                            
                         2, 1  ) as inter                                                             
                         ) a

select  atpt_ofcdc_sc_code, sd_schul_code, to_char(now(), 'YYYYMMDD') AS start_ymd
     FROM cd_ods.tb_sf_neis_school_info_t a, 
     (select max(seq) * 0 /5 + 1 as min_seq, max(seq) * ( 0 + 1) / 5 as max_seq from cd_ods.tb_sf_neis_school_info_t ) b
     WHERE COALESCE(TRIM(sd_schul_code), '') != '' AND seq BETWEEN b.min_seq AND b.max_seq
     and not exists (select 1 from cd_ods.tb_sf_neis_meal_service_diet_info_t c
					where c.atpt_ofcdc_sc_code = a.atpt_ofcdc_sc_code 
					  and c.sd_schul_code = a.sd_schul_code 
					  and c.mlsv_ymd >= to_char(now(), 'YYYYMMDD')
					);

select atpt_ofcdc_sc_code, sd_schul_code 
from cd_ods.tb_sf_neis_school_info_t
where (atpt_ofcdc_sc_code, sd_schul_code) not in 
(
select atpt_ofcdc_sc_code, sd_schul_code from cd_ods.tb_sf_neis_school_schedule_t 
)
and coalesce( trim(sd_schul_code),'') != '';

select min(a.work_date) as str_date
	,max(a.work_date) as end_date
from (
	select to_char(base_date,'yyyymmdd') as work_date
			,row_number() over (order by base_date) / (4)::int as rnum
		from cd_ods.aps_sdc_pw_mst a
			,(
				select distinct period
				from cd_ods.tb_jweshop_table_master                       
			) b
		where 1=1
		--and base_date between date('2022-04-17') and date('2024-08-12')
		and base_date between date('2024-08-29') and date('2024-09-01')
		and b.period = @{pipeline().parameters.period}
	) a	 
where  1=1  -- 
group by a.rnum
order by a.rnum
